query.name: getLastIduoValid
query.content: SELECT MAX(o.persistenceId) FROM OrgOrganisation o WHERE o.idUo = :idUo AND o.refus = false

query.name: getUo
query.content: SELECT o FROM OrgOrganisation o WHERE o.refus = false AND o.modif = false ORDER BY o.persistenceId ASC

query.name: getListeOrga
query.content: SELECT o FROM OrgOrganisation o WHERE o.codeDiv= :codeDiv AND o.refus = false AND o.modif = false ORDER BY o.persistenceId ASC

query.name: getTypeEntite
query.content: SELECT e FROM EnLType e WHERE e.libelleFR LIKE 'Etablis%' ORDER BY e.persistenceId ASC

query.name: getListeSociet
query.content: SELECT e FROM EnLEntiteJuridique e WHERE e.codeDiv = :codeDiv AND ( e.dateFin > CURRENT_TIMESTAMP OR e.dateFin is null ) ORDER BY e.persistenceId ASC

query.name: getListePers
query.content: SELECT p FROM PersRole p WHERE p.codeDiv = :codeDiv AND p.dateFin > CURRENT_DATE OR p.dateFin = null ORDER BY p.persistenceId ASC

query.name: findLibelleById
query.content: SELECT e FROM EnLGroupement e WHERE e.idEnLSociete = :idEnLSociete ORDER BY e.persistenceId ASC
